OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixed day of bright or sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers throughout the day.
OL,7,FShowers may be heavy and perhaps
OL,8,Fthundery at times before easing later
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe odd shower possible in
OL,12,Fthe evening but mainly dry with late
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells. Turning
OL,14,Fcloudier overnight with rain spreading
OL,15,Finto the west before dawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks
OL,18,Fof rain and drizzle, heavy at times.
OL,19,FRain most persistent in the morning
OL,20,Fbefore turning patchier with drier
OL,21,Fspells through the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
