OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and breezy with showers on
OL,7,FFriday and Saturday, showers mainly in
OL,8,Fthe west. A dry day on Sunday with
OL,9,Fsome long spells of sunshine
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
